   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Dioskourides to my sweetest sister Eudamonis, greeting. I salute you, sister, through this letter and I pray by all the gods that I will find you in good health as I come back. I approached the most splendid prefect. He received my case favourably and said he would hear (my case??) on the way down the Nile. And all the way  to Koptos I travel with the mighty Severus, and from there, if the gods will, I return to you. The wine, I think that the wine of the nom.... of Sinary has been sold for a good price. But if not of the best ... and the wine .....;Recto:;............................;To mye sister Eudaimonis from ........ Dioskourides</ab>
         </div>
